NG0792:1: mchog gsum tshang ba'i mtshams gcad la //
NG0792:2: man+dal mthing nag gru gsum la //
NG0792:3: phung sa gsum dang dug khrag sbru //
NG0792:4: lho ru rtse bstan rtsang mar bskor //
NG0792:5: sha chen snying snas gtor ma brgyan //
NG0792:6: mon pa'i thod dang dpa' bo'i rta /
NG0792:7: khyi spyang bya spre'i lug dang dar //
NG0792:8: rabs chad nag mo yug sa phag / nal bu rgya tshil bong bu sbrul //
NG0792:9: 'bras bu gcad dang don snying la //
NG0792:10: dregs pa'i dam rdzas gzung la dbye //
NG0792:11: lta ba chos nyid zab mo'i gdeng *//
NG0792:12: dbang rdzogs pa yi rdo rje'i gdeng *//
NG0792:13: ye shes lhun grub phyag rgya gsal //
NG0792:14: gcod pa spyi dang sgo yis gzer //
NG0792:15: gnod byed gzir ba de bzhin min //
NG0792:16: chos sku mnyam rdzogs gzir mi dgos //
NG0792:17: lo thog rkam chags 'khrul ba yi //
NG0792:18: dug lnga'i nad kyis zin pa la //
NG0792:19: bde ba'i stobs med zhen chags can //
NG0792:20: log pa'i stobs gzhom drag po gzir //
NG0792:21: gshin rje la sogs dregs pa yis //
NG0792:22: rang rang srog dag spyi srog dril //
NG0792:23: yi ge gnad kyis 'joms par byed /
NG0792:24: khams gsum dbang byed dregs pa can //
NG0792:25: dregs pa'i de nyid shes gyur na //
NG0792:26: dregs pa rang gshed rang gis byed //
NG0792:27: kun gyi srog snying e la sdud //
NG0792:28: 'bru gsum snying rtsa mgrin par gnas //
NG0792:29: 'bru gnyis mgo dang yan la gnas //
NG0792:30: gnod byed 'bru drug shes rgyud dbab //
NG0792:31: de la sngags kyi stobs kyi gzir //
NG0792:32: rang gshed phyag cha rang la bskor //
NG0792:33: lha rten bstan thub dgra la dbyung *//
NG0792:34: om a kro te ka ya man ta ka ha na ma tha b+han dza hu~m phat /
NG0792:35: bdag nyid sku gsung rdzogs par bsgom //
NG0792:36: stobs kyi drag sngags 'bum tsho bcu //
NG0792:37: snying sna dam rdzas gang 'grub dbye //
NG0792:38: spyi dril las dang rang rang dbye //
NG0792:39: myur dang stobs dpag med pa 'byung *//
NG0792:40: bsgrub bya rang gi shes rgyud la //
NG0792:41: rno dbal mtshon cha'i yi ge gnas //
NG0792:42: snying la nri gnas mgrin par hu~m //
NG0792:43: lte bar thugs dang gsang bar dza //
NG0792:44: klad par trig gnan mgo stengs nan //
NG0792:45: rtsa bzhi mdud pa 'bru bzhi gcod //
NG0792:46: mtshon cha'i rgyal po rno dbal ldan //
NG0792:47: rtsa srog shes rgyud dran pa gcod //
NG0792:48: de bskul mtshon cha rgyud la ldang *//
NG0792:49: stobs kyi sngags kyis 'phen par byed /
NG0792:50: e badzra sarba dush+tan mi trig nan //
NG0792:51: e hur thums dza ma ra ya rbad /
NG0792:52: de yi sbyor ba stobs zhan na //
NG0792:53: ming dang snying po 'bru re sbyar //
NG0792:54: 'bru bzhi mtshon cha'i stobs kyis gcad //
NG0792:55: las dang sbyor ba rtsa dang srog / thams cad 'dod dang mi 'jigs gcod //
NG0792:56: gang brtsams las la don med na //
NG0792:57: stobs dang bcas pa dril la rdeg / rang lus bstan pa'i shes rgyud las //
NG0792:59: rang lugs gnas pa'i go chas bsrung *//
NG0792:61: mtshon cha nag po sku'i rgyud las /
NG0792:62: rang gshed rang la dbab pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o
NG0792:63: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis drag sngags
NG0792:66: dun ya ma snying khrag ra dza ya /
NG0792:70: e ma ra ya rbad srog la e bam tsa sha ru hi nri ma ra ya rbad /
NG0792:72: srog la tsit+ta gu la nri ma ra ya rbad /
NG0792:73: srog la e bam ram yam kham nri ma ra ya rbad /
NG0792:74: srog la khyer chung kham shag ma ra ya rbad /
NG0792:80: srog la ki li ki la ya /
NG0792:86: mtshon cha nag po sku'i rgyud las /
NG0792:87: drag sngags bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o // //
NG0792:88: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi dregs pa chan la
NG0792:90: ngo bo ma bcos bde ba chen po'i ngang *//
NG0792:91: chos nyid ye nas lhun gyis grub //
NG0792:92: ye shes dkyil 'khor snang la rang bzhin med //
NG0792:93: sprul pa sna tshogs log rtog mkhas //
NG0792:94: tha snyad tshig rnams don gyis yang dag ston //
NG0792:95: de ltar rtogs nas sangs rgyas nyid yin pas //
NG0792:96: de la gsad dang gnan pa med //
NG0792:97: bden don ma rtogs sdug bsngal phung por smin //
NG0792:98: lus ngag sems kyi 'du byed kyis //
NG0792:99: gzhan pas lhag pas stobs rnyed pas //
NG0792:100: dregs pa'i lus ngag sems su snang *//
NG0792:101: gdug pa'i sems kyis gnod cing rngam //
NG0792:102: de la sngags kyi sbyor ba sdeb //
NG0792:103: dregs pa'i de nyid shes gyur na //
NG0792:104: dregs pa rang gshed rang gis byed //
NG0792:105: yi ge spyi yis gzir byas la //
NG0792:106: dregs pa'i rnam shes yig 'bru gcig / 'phrog byed yi ge 'bru gsum gyis //
NG0792:108: gcod byed mtshon cha 'bru bzhi yis //
NG0792:109: rang srog rang gis gcod par bye //
NG0792:110: dregs pa spyi yi las su bshad //
NG0792:111: dregs pa sgos kyis sbyor ba'i stobs //
NG0792:112: las dang nus par sbyar la gzud //
NG0792:113: gzir dang srog la rbad pa'i las //
NG0792:114: rang gnad gzhom pa 'di lta ste //
NG0792:115: zhi khro gshin rje phur pa dang *//
NG0792:116: ma mo bdud mo srin mo dang *//
NG0792:117: bdud dang mu stegs rgyal po btsan //
NG0792:118: dmu dang ru dra srin po dang *//
NG0792:119: gnod sbyin skyes bu ging dag dang *//
NG0792:120: phug bdag srid can gdug pa gsum //
NG0792:121: de nyid ma shes rang srog gcod //
NG0792:122: dregs pa'i phyag cha rang la 'khor //
NG0792:123: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gsang sngags 'di dag gsungs so //
NG0792:125: sarba sha trum e shri badzra kro d+ha /
NG0792:127: ma ma ru lu ma dun ting ki la ya rta /
NG0792:128: ti ra ti ka / ru tra /
NG0792:142: ru tri ru sa na ga phu /
NG0792:143: de sngags kyi grong khyer de /
NG0792:144: sngags pa nang 'gras pa'i lha 'dre rgyud la gnod pa dang */
NG0792:145: rtags dang sbyar zhing sngags kyi phyag cha rang la bskor //
NG0792:146: rtags rnams 'khrugs na stong srog gcig tu dril la gzir //
NG0792:147: bdun nam bcu bzhi nyi shu gcig / gsum @#//
NG0792:148: mam lnga ru drag po gtir //
NG0792:149: dang po rang bsgrub snying po drang *//
NG0792:150: klad du gzir zhing dgug par bya //
NG0792:151: bos shing gzir la srog snying dbrog / ming dang rnam shes 'bru bzhis gcod //
NG0792:152: tha ma gnan bsreg dam bdar gces //
NG0792:153: mtshon cha nag po sku'i rgyud las /
NG0792:154: dregs pa gzir ba'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o // //
NG0792:155: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gsad pa las kyis
NG0792:156: rang gshed mtshon cha rang bzlog gi 'khor lo 'di
NG0792:157: gsungs so // phungs pa'i 'brub khung mthing nag tu //
NG0792:158: mtshon cha dmar po'i srin mo khros //
NG0792:159: dur khrod ras sam rgya shog la //
NG0792:160: 'khor lo rim pa gsum pa ste //
NG0792:161: drag po dbang la 'khor lo brgyad //
NG0792:162: dregs pa gang bsgrub lto bar bca' //
NG0792:163: ming dang rnam shes bsgyur cing gsad //
NG0792:164: rang gshed rang la dbab cing bskor //
NG0792:165: de yang lus sems ma phyed na //
NG0792:166: dug lnga las kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NG0792:167: dug gsum shes pa ar la gtad /
NG0792:168: tsit+ta gnad la dbab cing gsad //
NG0792:169: 'byung ba dkrug pas phung po 'jig / rang sgrub
NG0792:170: dam can rang la bzlog / tsit+ta dkrug pa'i sngags
NG0792:171: dang sdeb // gshed po las rgyal lto bar gsad //
NG0792:172: 'gu ru seng ge'i khog mig gshig / dam tshig dang ldan sngags pa spyi //
NG0792:173: rdo rje spun dang a ting pa //
NG0792:174: las kyi skabs sbyar 'khor lo dkrug / 'di min las gzhan spug pas byang *//
NG0792:175: mtshon cha nag po sku'i rgyud las //
NG0792:176: gsad pa las kyi srog tig las kyi le'u ste
NG0792:177: lnga pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis
NG0792:178: skyin thang drag po chu 'khyags dbab pa 'di gsungs
NG0792:179: so // gnyan ra gdug pa'i gnas dag tu //
NG0792:180: rab chad thod pa spyang khu'i khrag / gsum pa khrag gis kha sa bsku /
NG0792:181: khrag tu yul mi srun pa gzhug / rta nag lug nag khyi dkar snying //
NG0792:182: ra dmar rgya bo sbrul gyi snying *//
NG0792:183: dri bo rabs chad nag po'i snying *//
NG0792:184: dam rdzas brten la sde brgyad rten //
NG0792:185: thod pa dum bur yugs sa rme //
NG0792:186: dri dang rnol gyi khrag blugs la //
NG0792:187: drag sngags 'bum tsho bcu re bstim //
NG0792:188: ta tsho gsum po me thabs tshul //
NG0792:189: yul gyi rkang mdun dbus su gzhug / dri dang bzlog sngags sngon du dbab //
NG0792:190: ma phebs sbyor ba stobs zhan na //
NG0792:191: sde brgyad snying po gnas nas dbrog / dmar nag dug khrag klong du bsdu //
NG0792:192: sngags rnams dkrugs la sde brgyad gzer //
NG0792:193: snying sna bsreg la 'og tu gzhug / gshin rje gshed dang stobs chen bsgom //
NG0792:194: snying po 'bru brgyad dbrog cing sdud //
NG0792:195: de yis cho dgod ri ltar gtibs //
NG0792:196: dril dang rtogs bsnol mar bsreg / de nas bcom
NG0792:197: ldan 'das kyis chu 'khyags dbab pa 'di gsungs so
NG0792:199: ma ma ya ma ra dza mu sa trig nan /
NG0792:200: ku ma hri ta phram phram shar shar kham hur thog phob /
NG0792:201: tri sa mu tsa da la ya /
NG0792:203: ya ma mu tsa dza tsa mun sa tri hur thums dza /
NG0792:204: tig nan phram phram hril hril kham shar hril hril b+h+yo su tri nan sa na kham @#//
NG0792:206: de yis 'khyags pa ri ltar spung *//
NG0792:207: ma phebs sbyor ba stobs chung na //
NG0792:208: zhing lpags rgyangs la gsum du bskor //
NG0792:209: dbus su thig bzhi le tshe brgyad //
NG0792:210: phyi rim rtsibs drug ya legs mtshon //
NG0792:212: phyogs bzhir stobs la mtshams bzhi srog / drug la srog dbrog gzer ba ste //
NG0792:213: tha mar mtshon cha 'bru bzhi gcod /
NG0792:214: kha sbyar bcas la drug mes bdug / des su las rnams 'grub par bshad //
NG0792:215: mtshon cha nag po sku'i rgyud las /
NG0792:216: chu 'khyags dbab pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o // //
NG0792:217: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dregs pa rnams kyi
NG0792:220: dregs pa tshogs kyis rtags bstan pa //
NG0792:221: mon dang zhib chen mdze can rnams //
NG0792:222: gshin rje yi ni rtags su bshad /
NG0792:223: khrag mtsho mon pa ma mo'i rtags //
NG0792:224: me 'bar phur pa na bur rtags //
NG0792:225: bya nag shin chen bdud kyi rtags //
NG0792:226: 'bag seng rtsad po rgyal po'i rtags //
NG0792:229: rje'u dang ban d+he dge bsnyen rtags //
NG0792:230: rta pa khyi spyang btsan gyi rtags /
NG0792:231: khyi dmar khrag mtsho the brang rtags //
NG0792:232: g.yag dang bon po mu stegs rtags //
NG0792:233: rgol dang khro na rbod gtong yin //
NG0792:234: las byed gar thabs sha la rol //
NG0792:235: ded ded rtags na thub pa'i rtags //
NG0792:236: rmi lam sna tshogs spyi yi rtags //
NG0792:237: dbang po mngon sum nang gi rtags //
NG0792:238: lus yang sems gsal gsang ba'i rtags //
NG0792:239: zhes pas rtags bzung 'khor lo bskor //
NG0792:240: gnam la shing lo gtibs pa'i sprin //
NG0792:241: bar snang sgra dang 'od dang me //
NG0792:242: sa la khrag rem sdo ma lud //
NG0792:243: dug rlangs 'chol ba skyin thang rtags //
NG0792:244: mtshon cha nag po sku'i rgyud las /
NG0792:245: rtags kyi le'u ste bdun pa'o // // de nas
NG0792:246: bcom ldan 'das kyis gnan pa'i las 'di gsungs so
NG0792:247: // gzhan gyi rbod gtong gnan pa dag / zhi khro ya ma phur pa ni //
NG0792:249: ma mo bdud mo srin mo rnams //
NG0792:250: bka' rten byin can 'og tu gnas //
NG0792:251: bdud dang mu stegs 'gong po rnams //
NG0792:252: ri khang sgo srungs 'og tu gnan //
NG0792:253: rgyal po dge bsnyen dkor srungs rnams /
NG0792:254: khyi tshangs la mkha'i 'og tu gnan //
NG0792:255: btsan dang srog bdag ri bo rnams //
NG0792:256: sha ru spyang thod gong gsum gnan //
NG0792:257: the brang chags 'gong gshin rdog rnams //
NG0792:258: glang ru bcug la lam mdor gnan //
NG0792:259: sa bdag klu gnyan mdze 'dren rnams //
NG0792:260: bka' sten byin can 'og tu gnan //
NG0792:262: sri can chu can them 'og gnan //
NG0792:263: srin po gdug pa'i thod pa la //
NG0792:264: ri rab rgya gram dang bcas la //
NG0792:265: thugs kyi snying po rab gnas la //
NG0792:266: gnan pa thod pa'i 'khor lor bshad //
NG0792:267: gri lcags phur gdug pa la //
NG0792:268: rdzas dgod bdug ste snying gdab //
NG0792:270: brgyad rdzas kyi du bas bdug / dregs pa gnad la dbab par bshad //
NG0792:271: bsreg pa me yi 'khor lo dag / me thab bcas la me lha bskyed //
NG0792:272: ling ga gdug la dug chu blugs //
NG0792:273: drag sngags brab cing bsreg par bya //
NG0792:274: las rnams rdzogs nas stong nyid la //
NG0792:275: dregs pa thams cad zhi bar 'gyur //
NG0792:276: phyis kyi dngos grub bsdu bar bya //
NG0792:277: lha la stong pa'i rgya yis gdab //
NG0792:279: de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NG0792:280: sngags thub gzir la dbab bya ba //
NG0792:281: thod khrag dug chu stong bskor tshad //
NG0792:282: ldan pa gsum gyi zor du 'phang *//
NG0792:283: nyungs kar thal chen rdo thun brab //
NG0792:284: gzugs dang thal ba dong du re //
NG0792:285: gnas pa gsang ba'i las su rig / ces gsungs so //
NG0792:287: las kyi mtha' sdud kyi le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NG0792:288: // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor la rgyud
NG0792:289: gtad pa // e ma rdo rje snying po che //
NG0792:290: nga yi bka' rgyud me lce 'di //
NG0792:291: rgyal ba kun gyi mdzad spyod de //
NG0792:292: kye ma rdo rje bsam dpag dka' //
NG0792:293: stong phrag bdun dang brgya phrag brgyad //
NG0792:294: snying po don gyi don bsdus pa'o //
NG0792:295: brjod pa kun grol bka' dang ldan //
NG0792:296: bde ba gcig gis bsgongs pa 'di //
NG0792:297: sangs rgyas spyod lam kun grol med //
NG0792:298: gab pa gsang ba'i lam chen 'di //
NG0792:299: rims can rdo rje snying pos bzung *//
NG0792:300: nga yi bka' yi gsang rgyud 'di //
NG0792:301: ma 'ongs dam can sgrub byed na //
NG0792:302: nga yang dam las ma yel srun //
NG0792:303: rdo rje bde ba'i rgyal po dang *//
NG0792:304: stobs dpag med pa'i khro tshogs kun //
NG0792:305: dam can sgrub byed bsrung zhing gnas //
NG0792:306: rgyud kyi snying po rab tu zungs //
NG0792:307: rnam rtogs mtshan ma rang grol ba'i //
NG0792:308: rdo rje rgyal po bde ba'i bka' //
NG0792:309: lcags thog spu gri rbad chen 'di //
NG0792:310: lha dang mkha' 'gro gsad pa yi //
NG0792:311: thun mong rigs dang thun mong kun //
NG0792:312: snying po sngags kyi gsang rgyud zung *//
NG0792:315: 'khor thams cad rjes su yi rangs te mngon par bstod do //
NG0792:316: drag sngags mtshon cha nag po sku'i rgyud las /
NG0792:317: rgyud gtad cing yi rang ba'i le'u ste dgu pa'o
NG0792:318: // // sde brgyad chan la 'bebs shing rang gshed
NG0792:320: rdo rje thogs 'bebs sku'i rgyud ces bya ba lha
NG0792:321: yul du grags pa rdzogs so // // bal po
NG0792:322: ba su da ra dang bod kyi sgra bsgyur gyi
NG0792:323: lo tsa ba slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes kyis
